14 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
15 SECTION 1. NEW LAW A new section of law to be codified
16 in the Oklahoma Statutes as Section 34.401 of Title 62, unless there
17 is created a duplication in numbering, reads as follows:
18 In addition to other duties imposed upon the Office of
19 Management and Enterprise Services (OMES) by law, the Director of
20 the Office of Management and Enterprise Services shall ensure that
21 the following procedures are strictly adhered to with respect to the
22 Oklahoma Department of Mental Health and Substance Abuse Services:
23 1. In accordance with paragraph 3 of subsection A of Section
24 34.6 of this title, prior to releasing the one-twelfth (1/12)
